  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/d741ceafe86e0e698d26bd0e4403245a.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/5035967b03b34133edf691007a6c9309.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forgotten village of Kanary awakens as you arrive. Is it truly abandoned… or hiding something? Uncover its dark secrets, outsmart the twisted priest, and snap the perfect shots—for your blog and your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/6f6d7a6f9eddb1555422b823ed966a0b.poster.avif?t=1757227105\" width=575 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/6f6d7a6f9eddb1555422b823ed966a0b.webm?t=1757227105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/55bd7adf6df176685d8124172b10d931.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Atmosphery terror:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a chilling atmosphere packed with unexpected jumpscares, cinematic scenes, and heart-racing tension. Every creak, whisper, and shadow keeps you on edge.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzles:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve twisted puzzles to uncover the chilling truth behind Kanary’s curse. Explore maze-like halls, secret chambers, and dark rituals. Will you survive long enough to stop the evil within? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >tep into a time of fear and superstition. Set during the witch trials, uncover hidden truths, solve ancient riddles, and survive a world where the line between witch and innocent is dangerously thin.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Our art:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've poured our heart and soul into creating a visual masterpiece, rich with Tim Burton-inspired artistry, designed to captivate and mesmerize at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/809e34536ebb219bf8a082d10b91b1eb.poster.avif?t=1757227105\" width=575 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/809e34536ebb219bf8a082d10b91b1eb.webm?t=1757227105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/4d714e3e40bfc1c48a07d07a1ab36d11.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charlie, a struggling photographer for the obscure horror blog \"Kanarian Horror,\" seeks to revive his career with a gripping story. Drawn to the forgotten village of Kanary, he ventures into its eerie ruins, only to feel a chilling presence: he’s not alone.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the village’s horrifying secrets. Solve twisted puzzles, evade the encroaching darkness, and face the malevolent priest that haunts Kanary. Will Charlie escape its grasp, or will he become another victim of its nightmarish hold?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/43a04a23c0a0d377c1a1bfd325a38d08.poster.avif?t=1757227105\" width=575 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/43a04a23c0a0d377c1a1bfd325a38d08.webm?t=1757227105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/114e490551bdaace8c7b82dd198d4190.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distribution is available to both individuals and corporations without permission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monetization is only possible when using the functions provided by the video distribution site.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We would appreciate it if you include the name of the game in the title of your video or live broadcast, or include a link to the Steam page in the summary section.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The contents of these guidelines are subject to change without notice.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/8bc3a2ef031599edad9f738bf63e657b.poster.avif?t=1757227105\" width=575 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/8bc3a2ef031599edad9f738bf63e657b.webm?t=1757227105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/5e6be006a5ddb785971462cfcdc35270.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bear Kanashi Ltd</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Is a enterprise of independent developer Kanashi, a 24-year-old who lives in the Canary Islands with his dog Bobbie. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590220/extras/b6828f866c9572ca55d364e5bdc93a00.avif?t=1757227105\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p>",
